# ShadcnUI Rules

## Core Principles
- Install ShadcnUI components in /packages/ui
- Always import components from @repo/ui, never directly from packages/ui
- Update the Tailwind preset or tokens in packages/ui (not per app)

## Component Patterns
- Use the class-variance-authority (cva) pattern for variants
- Use the cn utility for merging class names

```tsx
import { cn } from '@repo/utils'
import { cva } from 'class-variance-authority'

const buttonVariants = cva(
  'rounded-md font-medium transition-colors',
  {
    variants: {
      variant: {
        default: 'bg-primary text-white hover:bg-primary/90',
        secondary: 'bg-secondary text-white hover:bg-secondary/90'
      }
    },
    defaultVariants: {
      variant: 'default'
    }
  }
)
```

## Design System Organization
- Keep all core UI components in @repo/ui